sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_7ed3504c7be93900bc2526824b4d4dc8
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>MyUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var MyUtils = Class.create();
MyUtils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
	getSubjects : function() { // this function is not client callable
	
	var subjects = [];
	var existingSubjects = [];
	var rollNumber = this.getParameter('sysparm_rollNumber');
	var gr1 = new GlideRecord('u_exam_schedule');
	gr1.addQuery('u_roll_number',rollNumber);
	gr1.query();
	
	while(gr1.next())
		{
		existingSubjects.push(gr1.u_subjects.toString());
	}
	var gR = new GlideRecord('u_student_exam_registry');
	gR.addQuery('sys_id',rollNumber);
	gR.query();
	
	if(gR.next()){
		
		var gr = new GlideRecord('u_course_details');
		gr.addQuery('u_course',gR.u_course);
		gr.addQuery('u_semester',gR.u_semester);
		gr.addQuery('u_subjects','NOT IN',existingSubjects.toString());
		gr.query();
		while (gr.next()) {
			subjects.push(gr.u_subjects.toString());
		}
	}
	return subjects.toString();
}

});]]></script><sys_created_by>surya27</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-01-06 12:47:12</sys_created_on><sys_id>7ed3504c7be93900bc2526824b4d4dc8</sys_id><sys_mod_count>8</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>surya27</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-01-08 12:42:12</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include><sys_app_file action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><customer_update>true</customer_update><publish_override/><replace_on_upgrade>false</replace_on_upgrade><restore/><sys_app display_value="Online exam scheduler ">67937ecf7b49f500bc2526824b4d4d80</sys_app><sys_code>!!?D7/</sys_code><sys_created_by>surya27</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2015-01-06 12:47:12</sys_created_on><sys_id>af4a944c7be93900bc2526824b4d4deb</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>MyUtils</sys_name><sys_parent/><sys_path>!!?D7/</sys_path><sys_policy/><sys_source_deleted>false</sys_source_deleted><sys_source_id>7ed3504c7be93900bc2526824b4d4dc8</sys_source_id><sys_source_table>sys_script_include</sys_source_table><sys_type>code</sys_type><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_7ed3504c7be93900bc2526824b4d4dc8</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>surya27</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2015-01-08 12:42:12</sys_updated_on></sys_app_file></record_update>
